          "component_id": "story",
          "data": {
            "list": [
              {
                "desc": "A sturdy steel sword forged by the method of folding.</br>It has a dull shine with a cold glimmer.</br>It belonged to a famous adventurer who witnessed the vastness of the earth.</br>With it, he severed the iron bones of monsters and crossed blades with bandits.</br>But in the end,</br>He gave up the vast earth, the boundless sky,</br>His friends in the Guild, his trusty Cool Steel, and old pals, to be with the girl he loved.</br>",
                "title": ""
              }
            ]
          }
        }
